    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="support-vector-machine"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#support-vector-machine"></a> Support Vector Machine</h1><h2 id="前言"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#前言"></a> 前言</h2><p>SVM是一种非常重要的机器学习分类算法，在DeepLearning普及之前占据着分类算法主导地位，放在今天仍然有很多场景会用到SVM，这篇文章将详细讲解SVM，文末会有Matlab的SVM实现源码，方便读者理解其具体实现。</p><h2 id="svm简介"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#svm简介"></a> SVM简介</h2><p>SVM是一种有监督的机器学习算法，用来对两类数据进行分类。</p><p>整个SVM算法有以下几个重点：</p><ul><li>Margins</li><li>Primal</li><li>Lagrange</li><li>Dual</li><li>Soft Margin</li><li>Kernel</li></ul><p>在对SVM进行细节讲解之前，我们先弄清楚SVM到底在做什么。我们考虑这样一个例子，假设小明需要向银行申请贷款用来购房，银行需要决定是否批准小明的申请，在此之前银行都是通过 <strong>年龄-收入</strong> 来决定，并且银行有如下的历史数据：</p><p align="center">  <img width="400" height="400" src="https://github.com/lanxiang1017/lanxiang1017.github.io/raw/master/2020/01/08/SVM/svm1.png"></p><p>这时如果银行想通过以前的数据来决定是否批准小明的申请该怎么做呢，我们会很自然的想到在上述数据中划一个界限，如果小明落在这个界限的一边，则批准申请，否则拒绝，即如下图所示：</p><p align="center">  <img width="400" height="400" src="https://github.com/lanxiang1017/lanxiang1017.github.io/raw/master/2020/01/08/SVM/svm2.png"></p>我们划的这个界限也叫做Hyperplane。<blockquote><p>Hyperplane 是指在高维数据中的一个平面，在上图二维数据中这个hyperplane就可以是一条直线，一个Hyperplane可由<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">w</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>b</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\mathbf{w}, b)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf" style="margin-right:0.01597em;">w</span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>表示，可以写成<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">w</mi><mi>T</mi></msup><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">g(\mathbf{x})=\mathbf{w}^{T} \mathbf{x}+b=0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span></span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.924661em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf" style="margin-right:0.01597em;">w</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8413309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span><br />Hyperplane将对给定的点 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf{x}_{i}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.59444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 进行区分：</p><p class='katex-block katex-error' title='ParseError: KaTeX parse error: Can&#039;t use function &#039;$&#039; in math mode at position 222: …d{array}\right.$̲$如果Hyperplane正确…'>\operatorname{sgn}\left[g\left(\mathbf{x}_{i}\right)\right]=\left\{\begin{array}{lll}{+1} &amp; {\text { if }} &amp; {g\left(\mathbf{x}_{i}\right)&gt;0} \\{-1} &amp; {\text { if }} &amp; {g\left(\mathbf{x}_{i}\right)&lt;0}\end{array}\right.$$如果Hyperplane正确区分给定的数据，则</p></blockquote><p>\operatorname{sgn}\left[g\left(\mathbf{x}<em>{i}\right)\right]=d</em>{i} \quad \text { or } \quad \operatorname{sgn}\left[d_{i} g\left(\mathbf{x}_{i}\right)\right]=1</p><p class='katex-block katex-error' title='ParseError: KaTeX parse error: Expected &#039;EOF&#039;, got &#039;#&#039; at position 402: …来要介绍的Margins了#̲# MarginsMarg…'>**那么问题来了，以上数据中，Hyperplane只有一个吗？**答案很显然是不止一个，要知道我们划的这个Hyperplane可是会直接影响到小明的贷款申请，所以这个Hyperplane的好坏显得非常重要，如下图所示。 &lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;  &lt;img width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;400&quot; src=&quot;https://github.com/lanxiang1017/lanxiang1017.github.io/raw/master/2020/01/08/SVM/svm3.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;**那如何找到这个最优的界限(Hyperplane)呢？**这就是SVM需要做的事情，概括的说，**SVM提供了一种系统的方法来将数据最优化区分**。**我们如何定义这个最优的界限(Hyperplane)呢?**这就涉及到我们接下来要介绍的Margins了## MarginsMargin，也就是间隔，是SVM理论中非常关键的理念。Margin 总的来说有三类：* Functional Margin* Geometric Margin* Margin of a training set我们可以再细分：* $\gamma_{i}^{f}$ : Functional margin of an example $\mathbf({x_i, d_i})$* $\gamma_{i}^{g}$: Geometric margin of an example $\mathbf({x_i, d_i})$* $\gamma^{f}$: Functional margin of a training set* $\gamma^{g}$: Geometric margin of a training set* $\gamma$: Margin of a training set接下来我们看看每种Margin的数学定义及其物理意义给定一个Hyperplane $(\mathbf{w}, b)$：*1. Functional Margin $\gamma_{i}^{f}$ of an example $\mathbf({x_i, d_i})$*$$\gamma_{i}^{f}=d_{i}\left(\mathbf{w}^{T} \mathbf{x}_{i}+b\right)</p><p><em>2. Geometric margin <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>γ</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>g</mi></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\gamma_{i}^{g}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.059164em;vertical-align:-0.276864em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7823em;"><span style="top:-2.4231360000000004em;margin-left:-0.05556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.1809080000000005em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.276864em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> of an example <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathbf({x_i, d_i})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></em></p><p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>γ</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>g</mi></msubsup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∥</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">w</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∥</mi></mrow></mfrac><msup><mi mathvariant="bold">w</mi><mi>T</mi></msup><msub><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∥</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">w</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∥</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi>b</mi><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\gamma_{i}^{g}=d_{i}\left(\frac{1}{\|\mathbf{w}\|} \mathbf{w}^{T} \mathbf{x}_{i}+\frac{1}{\|\mathbf{w}\|} b\right)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.059164em;vertical-align:-0.276864em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7822999999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.4231360000000004em;margin-left:-0.05556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.180908em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.276864em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.40003em;vertical-align:-0.95003em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;"><span class="delimsizing size3">(</span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.32144em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">∥</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf" style="margin-right:0.01597em;">w</span></span><span class="mord">∥</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.936em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf" style="margin-right:0.01597em;">w</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8913309999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.32144em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">∥</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf" style="margin-right:0.01597em;">w</span></span><span class="mord">∥</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.936em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mord mathdefault">b</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;"><span class="delimsizing size3">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><p>可以证明<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>γ</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>g</mi></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\gamma_{i}^{g}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.059164em;vertical-align:-0.276864em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7823em;"><span style="top:-2.4231360000000004em;margin-left:-0.05556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.1809080000000005em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.276864em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的物理意义是点<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{x_i}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.58056em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>到我们给定的Hyperplane的欧式距离，数学证明之后会放在附录里，这里我们先重点关注其意义。</p><p align="center">  <img width="400" height="400" src="https://github.com/lanxiang1017/lanxiang1017.github.io/raw/master/2020/01/08/SVM/svm5.png"></p><p>根据数学定义，我们可以发现<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><msubsup><mi>γ</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>f</mi></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\gamma_{i}^{f}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2438799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.276864em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05556em;">γ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9670159999999999em;"><span style="top:-2.4231360000000004em;margin-left:-0.05556em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span sty